[38.546919, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1m\u001b[96mBrainyard TUI\u001b[0m\u001b[2m — \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[36mtodo-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[95mclaude-code/opus\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[2msession tutorial-06-todos\u001b[0m \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2mType /help for commands. AI output may be inaccurate.\u001b[0m                     \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ Following the plan to add a --quiet flag to a CLI tool (add --quiet/-q to the arg parse"]
[38.546927, "o", "r, propagate it through a conf...\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(41206 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(29.1s)\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThis is a SPAWN request. Normally C1 (PLAN DOSSIER) would GATHER since :agent-context is \u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mjust \"system-context\" with no `Saved dossier:` path. But the user explicitly provides the \u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mfull plan inline (7 ordered approach bullets) AND instructs \"Do not ask for more context.\" \u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mThat is an effective :plan-ok? override — the inline plan is the source of truth. \u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mPRE-FLIGHT therefore = GO: C5 passes (7 approach bullets decompose well), acceptance \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mcriteria derive cleanly from the 7 plan steps. I'll AUTHOR a concrete ordered todo, then \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mPOST-FLIGHT, then PERSIST a dossier — and STOP (no exec-agent dispatch). Acceptance \u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mcriteria (A1–A7) map to the 7 plan "]
[38.54694, "o", "steps. Let me author the todo via doc$create with \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mverb-led, atomically-markable items, each tagged with :via and :covers.\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠙\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mPondering...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (29.1s)\u001b[0m"]
